name: Economics 101 Bear Market
description:
The second instalment of the
"Economics 101" series. A bear market
is a place where you chill with bears
and drink a pint of hot chocolate. My
little family altogether; bears, cats, a
goose and my beloved fox just doing a
casual black market activity. We don't
know anything about missing
astronauts. No astronaut harmed in
the process of making. 18 seconds
seamless loop, 1500x1500 px 4K
available upon request . Design,
animation and SFX by Piano and the
Fox( me <3) No external 3d models
being used.. Music by Shane Iver
